  "pqrsEmpty": "You don't have any requests in your history yet.",
  "helpBody1a": "You can open VibeTours as a guest to explore approved tours, nearby places, the basic map and public details.",
  "helpBody1b": "To create tours, save favorites in the cloud, comment, rate, send PQRS or request availability you need to log in.",
  "helpBody1c": "If you try a private action, VibeTours will show the warning 'Log in to continue' without losing what you were seeing.",
  "helpBody1d": "Email login remains available. If Google is configured, you can also log in with your Google account.",
  "helpBody2a": "The Discover section shows highlighted places using your location and nearby recommendations.",
  "helpBody2b": "If the search engine is empty, you will see popular or nearby recommendations so that the screen is never empty of content.",
  "helpBody2c": "You can search for words like museum, restaurant, park, beach or viewpoint to find real places.",
  "helpBody2d": "Use filters for category, price, distance and suitable for minors to adjust the results.",
  "helpBody3a": "Explore tours created by the community or generated by our AI.",
  "helpBody3b": "Use the top search bar to search for tours by name or keyword.",
  "helpBody3c": "Tap the filter icon to adjust the search by category, price and more.",
  "helpBody4a": "View tourist places, events and points of interest directly on the map.",
  "helpBody4b": "Tap on the pins to see a quick card of the place.",
  "helpBody4c": "By touching a card, the detail of the place will open where you can save it, ask for availability if it is a restaurant/hotel, or start the route there.",
  "helpBody5a": "Create your own tours by adding a name, description and cover image.",
  "helpBody5b": "Add stops (places) by searching them in our database connected to maps.",
  "helpBody5c": "You can define how many people and how many days the tour lasts.",
  "helpBody6a": "Generate a complete tour simply by describing what you want to see and do with the AI.",
  "helpBody6b": "You can use advanced options to specify if it lasts days or hours.",
  "helpBody6c": "Once the tour is generated, you can save it in your account or edit it to add or remove stops before saving it.",
  "helpBody7a": "You can edit your created tours in the 'My Tours' section.",
  "helpBody7b": "Save your favorite places and organize them to consult them quickly.",
  "helpBody8a": "Complete your tourist profile by choosing your favorite interests and categories.",
  "helpBody8b": "Change your photo, name and preferences for language and visual theme.",
  "helpBody9a": "Send Petitions, Complaints, Claims and Suggestions directly from the app.",
  "helpBody9b": "Check the status of your PQRS and administrator responses in the 'History' tab.",
  "privSec1Title": "Data we collect",
  "privSec1Body": "We can process email, user identifier, display name, profile picture, biography, tourist preferences, favorites, created tours, completed tours, tour rating, PQRS history, approximate location and technical device data necessary to operate and optimize the app.",
  "privSec2Title": "Use of location and permissions",
  "privSec2Body": "Precise or approximate location is used to calculate local weather, nearby places, area events, progress during a tour, remaining distance and real-time recommendations. You can revoke permission from system settings, although some functions will depend on manual location.",
  "privSec3Title": "Artificial Intelligence and Recommendations",
  "privSec3Body": "Requests to the AI planner can include destination, city, country, duration, tour type, language and free text. We use these data anonymously to generate logical routes, descriptions, stops and images. We do not share your personal data with AI providers, only search parameters.",
  "privSec4Title": "Storage, Security and Synchronization",
  "privSec4Body": "Your account data and preferences (currency, language, achievements) are securely stored in Supabase with row-level security (RLS) policies. The mobile app only uses public keys for access, ensuring that your data is protected against unauthorized access.",
  "privSec5Title": "Shared and Public Content",
  "privSec5Body": "If you decide to publish tours, leave comments, ratings or send PQRS, this content will be associated with your account. Tours marked as private and drafts will not be visible to the community.",
  "privSec6Title": "Third parties and Analytics",
  "privSec6Body": "We can share anonymized data with analytics services to understand how the application is used and improve our recommendation algorithms. We will never sell your data to third parties for advertising purposes.",
  "privSec7Title": "Data retention and deletion",
  "privSec7Body": "We keep your data as long as your account is active or necessary to provide the service, security, support and legal obligations. You can request a copy of your data or its definitive deletion through the PQRS module or by contacting technical support.",
  "termsSec1Title": "Acceptance and Use of the application",
  "termsSec1Body": "By using VIBETOURS, you accept these terms in their entirety. The app offers discovery, creation and touring of tourist tours. The user agrees to use the app responsibly, respecting local regulations, the environment and avoiding restricted areas, private or dangerous properties.",
  "termsSec2Title": "Accuracy of Maps, Routes and Prices",
  "termsSec2Body": "Maps, times, distances, routes and prices (even converted to different currencies) are reference estimates. There may be closures, schedule changes, exchange rate variations, adverse weather or risks. Always verify information with official sources before traveling or making purchases.",
  "termsSec3Title": "AI Generated Content (VibeTour AI)",
  "termsSec3Body": "Tours generated by our Artificial Intelligence are automated recommendations based on tourist databases. Although we strive to offer real places and coherent routes, VIBETOURS does not guarantee its absolute accuracy. The user must validate schedules, accessibility and real existence of the place.",
  "termsSec4Title": "Intellectual Property and Copyright",
  "termsSec4Body": "All original content of the app belongs to VIBETOURS. By creating and publishing a tour on our platform, you grant us a non-exclusive license to display, promote and adapt it within the service.",
  "termsSec5Title": "User Responsibility and Risks",
  "termsSec5Body": "Outdoor tourism involves inherent risks. The user is solely responsible for their safety, health, belongings and behavior. VIBETOURS does not act as a travel agency nor replaces official guides, authorities or emergency services.",
  "termsSec6Title": "Tour Publishing and Review Guidelines",
  "termsSec6Body": "It is strictly prohibited to publish false, defamatory, offensive, discriminatory, dangerous, spam content or that infringes copyrights or privacy. VIBETOURS reserves the right to moderate, hide or remove content and suspend accounts that violate these rules.",
  "termsSec7Title": "Support, Claims and PQRS",
  "termsSec7Body": "All petitions, complaints, claims and suggestions must be channeled through the PQRS module integrated in the app. The target response time is less than 24 business hours, subject to technical availability and complexity of the requirement.",
  "helpBody4d": "When you start a tour, the map will show you the progress and remaining distance to each stop.",
  "helpBody7c": "Save other users' tours in your favorites to access them quickly.",
  "helpBody8c": "Your preferences are used to customize recommendations in the Discover section and in AI generation.",
  "helpBody9c": "You can check the status of your requests in the PQRS history.",
